  "title": "Url sync",
  "body": "This is the widget that will synchronize the search state with the URL.\n\nTwo implementations will be available : modern history API based and hashchange based. They will be slightly different because hashChange doesn't support to update the url/hash state.\n\nTODO : \n- [x] hashChange based implementation\n- [x] feature detection of the modern history API\n- [x] detect user parameters and searchParameters and avoid overriding them\n- [x] documentation\n",
